data.description: ALMOST 8 ACRES ZONED AGRICULTURAL IN ONE OF THE MOST DESIRED NEIGHBORHOODS IN WAYCROSS! Subdivide or keep it all for yourself! This home is the opportunity of a lifetime with great bones and a canvas for you to make it your own! Newer roof, new joists and new subfloor. Almost 3500 square feet of living space. Enter through the private gate into a paradise that is set back from it all. Main living area has a gas fireplace for those cozy nights. 4 large bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, saltwater pool with chlorine generator AND A POOL HOUSE WITH A BATHROOM! Formal living room, formal dining room, great room and additional enclosed sunroom. Guest house that you can also finish and design to your personal touches. Workshop/outbuilding for man-cave, she-cave or all your toys and storage shed! HUGE firepit for relaxing around with friends and family. This home is an entertainer's dream! Large oversized 4 car carport. Many fruit trees throughout the property and also grape vines! The current zoning is AG-1 for horses and other farm animals. This property is a great investment once it's finished to your desired colors and finishes. So much potential with this one.
